source.name: NSF Freedom of Information Act Report for October 1, 2007 through September 30, 2008
source.description: This file contains the National Science Foundation's 2008 FOIA Annual Report. The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 2008. It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
